  "description": "A close-up, vibrant image captures the interior of a white tulip in full bloom. The petals are a creamy, almost translucent white, gently curving inwards to reveal a bright yellow center. The stamen and pistil are visible, displaying a delicate green hue against the bold yellow backdrop. The lighting is soft and diffused, highlighting the delicate textures of the flower. A blurred green background suggests foliage, creating a shallow depth of field and drawing attention to the tulip's intricate details. The overall impression is one of fragility and natural beauty.",
